00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:42.000
This hairstyle is suitable for all age groups.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:51.000
First step, tie a pony tail and position it where you desire your updo bun to be.

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:59.000
Now use your donut bun like a rubber band 

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:08.000
and pull all you hair inside the bun like this.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Now move the donut bun till the edge of your hair 

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:20.000
and roll the ends of your hair inside the bun as shown

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.000
keep rolling the bun and spread your hair around the bun,

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:30.000
and make sure your hair covers the bun completely.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:35.000
Roll until your rubber band is covered.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:39.000
I am not using bobby pins or U pins to secure my bun,

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:45.000
but you can always use bobby pins if you feel the need for your hair.

